lead_paragraph: HOLZMANN-LANE--Edith, M.D.,passed away January 26, 2016. Devoted wife of the late Dr. Leo Holzmann and the late Fred Lane, beloved sister of the late Walter Gutmann. Dedicated physician, practiced for many years in Flushing, NY. Funeral service January 28, 2016 at Sinai Chapels. Contribution may be made to charity of your choice. 1/3

headline.main: Paid Notice: Deaths  HOLZMANN, LANE, EDITH, M.D.
